{"html":"<br/>\n<h2>Fact Symbols with Injective Instances</h2><br/>\n<p class=\"monospace rules\">None</p><br/>\n<h2>Multiset Rewriting Rules</h2><br/>\n<p class=\"monospace rules\"><span class=\"hl_keyword\">rule</span> (<span class=\"hl_keyword\">modulo</span> AC) isend:<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> !KU( x ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">--[</span> K( x ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]-&gt;</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> In( x ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_comment\">/* has exactly the trivial AC variant */</span><br/>\n<br/>\n<br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">rule</span> (<span class=\"hl_keyword\">modulo</span> AC) irecv:<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> Out( x ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">--&gt;</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> !KD( x ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_comment\">/* has exactly the trivial AC variant */</span><br/>\n<br/>\n<br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">rule</span> (<span class=\"hl_keyword\">modulo</span> E) ChanOut_S:<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> Out_S( $A, $B, x ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">--[</span> ChanOut_S( $A, $B, x ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]-&gt;</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> !Sec( $A, $B, x ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_comment\">/* has exactly the trivial AC variant */</span><br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">rule</span> (<span class=\"hl_keyword\">modulo</span> E) ChanIn_S:<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> !Sec( $A, $B, x ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">--[</span> ChanIn_S( $A, $B, x ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]-&gt;</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> In_S( $A, $B, x ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_comment\">/* has exactly the trivial AC variant */</span><br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">rule</span> (<span class=\"hl_keyword\">modulo</span> E) ChanOut_A:<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> Out_A( $A, x ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">--[</span> ChanOut_A( $A, x ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]-&gt;</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> !Auth( $A, x ), Out( &lt;$A, x&gt; ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_comment\">/* has exactly the trivial AC variant */</span><br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">rule</span> (<span class=\"hl_keyword\">modulo</span> E) ChanIn_A:<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> !Auth( $A, x ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">--[</span> ChanIn_A( $A, x ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]-&gt;</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> In_A( $A, x ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_comment\">/* has exactly the trivial AC variant */</span><br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">rule</span> (<span class=\"hl_keyword\">modulo</span> E) publickeyinfrastructure:<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> Fr( ~skX ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">--[</span> LongtermKey( $X, ~skX ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]-&gt;</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> !Ltk( $X, ~skX ), !Pk( $X, pk(~skX) ), Out( pk(~skX) ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_comment\">/* has exactly the trivial AC variant */</span><br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">rule</span> (<span class=\"hl_keyword\">modulo</span> E) Setup:<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> !Ltk( &#39;S&#39;, ~skS ), Fr( ~x1 ), Fr( ~x2 ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">--[</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;Setup( ), HV( &#39;1&#39;, h(&lt;~x1, $ind1&gt;) ),<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;HV( &#39;2&#39;, h(&lt;~x2, $ind2&gt;) ),<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;HY( &#39;1&#39;, h(~x1) ), HY( &#39;2&#39;, h(~x2) ),<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;V( &#39;1&#39;, &#39;empty&#39; ), V( &#39;2&#39;, $v2 ),<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;X( ~x1, ~x2 )<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">]-&gt;</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;AgSt_H0( &#39;H1&#39;,<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;&#39;D1&#39;, &#39;S&#39;, &#39;BB&#39;, &#39;empty&#39;, <br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;h(&lt;&#39;H1&#39;, ~x1&gt;)&gt;<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;),<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;AgSt_H0( &#39;H2&#39;,<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;&#39;D2&#39;, &#39;S&#39;, &#39;BB&#39;, $v2, <br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;h(&lt;&#39;H2&#39;, ~x2&gt;)&gt;<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;),<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;AgSt_D0( &#39;D1&#39;,<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;&#39;S&#39;, &#39;BB&#39;, &#39;H1&#39;, pk(~skS), ~x1, $ind1<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&gt;<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;),<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;AgSt_D0( &#39;D2&#39;,<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;&#39;S&#39;, &#39;BB&#39;, &#39;H2&#39;, pk(~skS), ~x2, $ind2<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&gt;<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;),<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;AgSt_BB0( &#39;BB&#39;,<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;&#39;ySG&#39;, <br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;(h(&lt;&#39;H1&#39;, ~x1&gt;)++h(&lt;&#39;H2&#39;, ~x2&gt;))&gt;<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;),<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;AgSt_Au( &#39;A&#39;, &#39;S&#39; ),<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Out_A( &#39;BB&#39;,<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;&#39;ySG&#39;, <br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;(h(&lt;&#39;H1&#39;, ~x1&gt;)++h(&lt;&#39;H2&#39;, ~x2&gt;))&gt;<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;),<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Out( &lt;~skS, &#39;H1&#39;, &#39;H2&#39;, &#39;D1&#39;, <br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#39;D2&#39;, ~x1, ~x2, $ind1, $ind2, &#39;BB&#39;&gt;<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;)<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_comment\">/* has exactly the trivial AC variant */</span><br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">rule</span> (<span class=\"hl_keyword\">modulo</span> E) H_1:<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> AgSt_H0( $H, &lt;$D, $S, $BB, vote, y&gt; ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">--[</span> Vote( $H, vote ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]-&gt;</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;AgSt_H1( $H, &lt;$D, $S, $BB, vote, y&gt; ), Out_S( $H, $D, vote )<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_comment\">/* has exactly the trivial AC variant */</span><br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">rule</span> (<span class=\"hl_keyword\">modulo</span> E) D_1:<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;AgSt_D0( $D, &lt;$S, $BB, $H, pkS, ~x, $ind&gt; ),<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;In_S( $H, $D, vote )<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">--&gt;</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Out_S( $D, $H,<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;$H, <br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;cp(&lt;vote, h(&lt;~x, $ind&gt;)&gt;, pkS), <br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;cp(&lt;h(&lt;$H, ~x&gt;), h(~x)&gt;, pkS)&gt;, <br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;$ind&gt;<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;)<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_comment\">// loop breaker: [1]</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_comment\">/* has exactly the trivial AC variant */</span><br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">rule</span> (<span class=\"hl_keyword\">modulo</span> E) H_2_abstain:<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;AgSt_H1( $H, &lt;$D, $S, $BB, &#39;empty&#39;, y&gt; ),<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;In_S( $D, $H, &lt;$H, code, ind&gt; )<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">--[</span> MyCode( $H, code ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]-&gt;</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> AgSt_H2( $H, &lt;$D, $S, $BB, &#39;empty&#39;, y, ind, code&gt; )<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_comment\">/* has exactly the trivial AC variant */</span><br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">rule</span> (<span class=\"hl_keyword\">modulo</span> E) H_2:<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;AgSt_H1( $H, &lt;$D, $S, $BB, vote, y&gt; ),<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;In_S( $D, $H, &lt;$H, code, ind&gt; )<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">--[</span> MyCode( $H, code ), Comm_H_V( $H, $S, vote ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]-&gt;</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;AgSt_H2( $H, &lt;$D, $S, $BB, vote, y, ind, code&gt; ),<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Out( &lt;code, ind&gt; )<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_comment\">/* has exactly the trivial AC variant */</span><br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">rule</span> (<span class=\"hl_keyword\">modulo</span> E) BB:<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;AgSt_BB0( $BB, ySG ),<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;In( &lt;&#39;votes&#39;, ($vote1++$vote2)&gt; ),<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;In( &lt;&#39;pVs&#39;, (pV1++pV2)&gt; ),<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;In( &lt;&#39;pYs&#39;, (pY1++pY2)&gt; ),<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;In( &lt;&#39;yPrime&#39;, (yPrime1++yPrime2)&gt; ),<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;In( &lt;&#39;codes&#39;, (code1++code2)&gt; ),<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;In( &lt;&#39;proofV&#39;, proofV&gt; ),<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;In( &lt;&#39;proofY&#39;, proofY&gt; )<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">--[</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;BB_V( &#39;1&#39;, $BB, $vote1 ), BB_V( &#39;2&#39;, $BB, $vote2 ),<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;BB_pV( &#39;1&#39;, $BB, pV1 ), BB_pV( &#39;2&#39;, $BB, pV2 ),<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;BB_yPrime( &#39;1&#39;, $BB, yPrime1 ),<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;BB_yPrime( &#39;2&#39;, $BB, yPrime2 ),<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;BB_pY( &#39;1&#39;, $BB, pY1 ), BB_pY( &#39;2&#39;, $BB, pY2 ),<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;BB_C( &#39;1&#39;, $BB, code1 ), BB_C( &#39;2&#39;, $BB, code2 ),<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;BB_Cs( $BB, &lt;&#39;codes&#39;, (code1++code2)&gt; ),<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;BB_proofV( $BB, proofV ), BB_proofY( $BB, proofY )<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">]-&gt;</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Out_A( $BB, &lt;&#39;votes&#39;, ($vote1++$vote2)&gt; ),<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Out_A( $BB, &lt;&#39;pVs&#39;, (pV1++pV2)&gt; ),<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Out_A( $BB, &lt;&#39;pYs&#39;, (pY1++pY2)&gt; ),<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Out_A( $BB, &lt;&#39;yPrime&#39;, (yPrime1++yPrime2)&gt; ),<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Out_A( $BB, &lt;&#39;codes&#39;, (code1++code2)&gt; ),<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Out_A( $BB, &lt;&#39;proofV&#39;, proofV&gt; ),<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Out_A( $BB, &lt;&#39;proofY&#39;, proofY&gt; )<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_comment\">/* has exactly the trivial AC variant */</span><br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">rule</span> (<span class=\"hl_keyword\">modulo</span> E) auditor:<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;AgSt_Au( $A, $S ), In_A( $BB, &lt;&#39;ySG&#39;, (y1++y2)&gt; ),<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;In_A( $BB, &lt;&#39;yPrime&#39;, (y1++y2)&gt; ),<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;In_A( $BB, &lt;&#39;votes&#39;, (v1++v2)&gt; ),<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;In_A( $BB,<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;&#39;pVs&#39;, (&lt;v1, hV1&gt;++&lt;v2, hV2&gt;)&gt;<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;),<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;In_A( $BB,<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;&#39;pYs&#39;, (&lt;y1, hY1&gt;++&lt;y2, hY2&gt;)&gt;<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;),<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;In_A( $BB,<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;&#39;codes&#39;, <br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;(&lt;fstcode1, sndcode1&gt;++&lt;fstcode2, sndcode2&gt;)&gt;<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;),<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;In_A( $BB, &lt;&#39;proofV&#39;, proofV&gt; ),<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;In_A( $BB, &lt;&#39;proofY&#39;, proofY&gt; )<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">--[</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;Learn_A_Vs( $S, $A, &lt;&#39;votes&#39;, (v1++v2)&gt; ),<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;Learn_A_YSGs( $S, $A, &lt;&#39;ySG&#39;, (y1++y2)&gt; ),<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;Learn_A_Cs( $S, $A,<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;&#39;codes&#39;, <br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;(&lt;fstcode1, sndcode1&gt;++&lt;fstcode2, sndcode2&gt;)&gt;<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;),<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;VerProofV( $A, $BB, proofV, &lt;fstcode1, fstcode2&gt;,<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;&lt;v1, hV1&gt;, v2, hV2&gt;<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;),<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;VerProofY( $A, $BB, proofY, &lt;sndcode1, sndcode2&gt;,<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;&lt;y1, hY1&gt;, y2, hY2&gt;<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;)<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">]-&gt;</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_comment\">/* has exactly the trivial AC variant */</span><br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">rule</span> (<span class=\"hl_keyword\">modulo</span> E) H_3:<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;AgSt_H2( $H, &lt;$D, $S, $BB, vote, y, ind, code&gt; ),<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;In_A( $BB, &lt;&#39;codes&#39;, (codeBBOther++mycodeBB)&gt; )<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">--[</span> Learn_H_C( $H, $S, mycodeBB ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">]-&gt;</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">[</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">]</span><br/>\n<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_comment\">/* has exactly the trivial AC variant */</span></p><br/>\n<h2>Restrictions of the Set of Traces</h2><br/>\n<p class=\"monospace rules\"><span class=\"hl_keyword\">restriction</span> OneSetup:<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&quot;<span class=\"hl_operator\">∀ </span>#i #j<span class=\"hl_operator\">.</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">(</span><span class=\"hl_operator\">(</span>Setup( ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">@</span> #i<span class=\"hl_operator\">)</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">∧</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">(</span>Setup( ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">@</span> #j<span class=\"hl_operator\">)</span><span class=\"hl_operator\">)</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">⇒</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">(</span>#i <span class=\"hl_operator\">=</span> #j<span class=\"hl_operator\">)</span>&quot;<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_comment\">// safety formula</span><br/>\n<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_comment\">/*<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;expanded formula:<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&quot;<span class=\"hl_operator\">∀ </span>#i #j<span class=\"hl_operator\">.</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">(</span><span class=\"hl_operator\">(</span>Setup( ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">@</span> #i<span class=\"hl_operator\">)</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">∧</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">(</span>Setup( ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">@</span> #j<span class=\"hl_operator\">)</span><span class=\"hl_operator\">)</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">⇒</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">(</span>#i <span class=\"hl_operator\">=</span> #j<span class=\"hl_operator\">)</span>&quot;<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;*/</span><br/>\n<br/>\n<span class=\"hl_keyword\">restriction</span> NotSendEmpty:<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&quot;<span class=\"hl_operator\">∀ </span>#i H S<span class=\"hl_operator\">.</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">(</span>Comm_H_V( H, S, &#39;empty&#39; ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">@</span> #i<span class=\"hl_operator\">)</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">⇒</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">(</span><span class=\"hl_operator\">⊥</span><span class=\"hl_operator\">)</span>&quot;<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_comment\">// safety formula</span><br/>\n<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_comment\">/*<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;expanded formula:<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&quot;<span class=\"hl_operator\">∀ </span>#i H S<span class=\"hl_operator\">.</span><br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"hl_operator\">(</span>Comm_H_V( H, S, &#39;empty&#39; ) <span class=\"hl_operator\">@</span> #i<span class=\"hl_operator\">)</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">⇒</span> <span class=\"hl_operator\">(</span><span class=\"hl_operator\">⊥</span><span class=\"hl_operator\">)</span>&quot;<br/>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;*/</span></p><br/>\n","title":"Multiset rewriting rules and restrictions"}